### **Material Information Summary**  
**Document Type:** *Appendix 2A – Quotation of New Securities*  

- **Security Issuance:**  
  - **699,999 new fully paid ordinary shares (BB1)** applied for quotation.  
  - **Issue price:** AUD **$0.30 per share**.  
  - **Issue date:** **09/07/2025**.  
  - Part of a **placement to directors and CEO**, approved by shareholders (referenced ASX announcement: [30-May-2025](https://announcements.asx.com.au/asxpdf/20250530/pdf/06k8l5hpnm8l52.pdf)).  

- **Post-Issuance Capital Structure:**  
  - **Quoted ordinary shares (BB1):** **87,261,155** (post-issuance).  
  - **Unquoted securities:** Includes **performance rights, restricted shares, and options** (detailed in Part 4.2 of the document).  

**Note:** No new capital raised disclosed here (transaction was pre-announced via Appendix 3B on **01-May-2025**). Focus is on **liquidity impact** from new shares quoted.  

**Omitted:** Distribution schedule (empty), director names, legal boilerplate.
